flowchart TD
    A[Tradie Opens App] --> B[View Dashboard]
    B --> C{Choose Action}
    C -->|New Job| D[Create Job Quote]
    C -->|Track Work| E[Log Hours & Materials]
    C -->|Send Invoice| F[Generate Invoice]
    C -->|Check Payments| G[View Payment Status]
    
    D --> D1[Enter Client Info]
    D1 --> D2[Add Services & Pricing]
    D2 --> D3[Send Quote to Client]
    D3 --> D4[Quote Accepted?]
    D4 -->|Yes| H[Job Active]
    D4 -->|No| B
    
    E --> E1[Record Work Completed]
    E1 --> E2[Add Material Costs]
    E2 --> E3[Update Job Status]
    E3 --> H
    
    H --> F
    F --> F1[Auto-Generate Invoice]
    F1 --> F2[Review & Customize]
    F2 --> F3[Send to Client]
    F3 --> F4[Invoice Sent]
    
    G --> G1[View Invoice Status]
    G1 --> G2[Track Payments Received]
    G2 --> G3[Overdue Alerts]
    G3 --> G4[Send Reminders]
    G4 --> G5[Mark as Paid]
    
    F4 --> I[Job Complete]
    G5 --> I
    I --> J[Archived in Records]
    J --> B
